author: akarasulu
msg: Major issue forcing me to have to bump up to MINA SNAPSHOTs.  This is due
to common dependencies between MINA and ApacheDS in shared-asn1 and shared-ldap.
Basically we had to bump up the revisions here due to some bugs and could
not stick to the 0.9.4 release for these deps.  But mina 0.9.1 asn1 has deps
on 0.9.4 of shared asn1 which causes a nasty issue when now having deps on
asn1 0.9.4 via mina and 0.9.5 via ApacheDS.  We have to bump up and try to cut
another mina release I think.  Darn it sorry about this we slipped.
